OL,3,CFour found guilty of murder of woman
OL,4,Cshot on doorstep
OL,6,FFour people have been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurder after a woman was fatally shot
OL,8,Fat a property in south Wales last year.
OL,10,FJoanne Penney, 40, was shot at point-
OL,11,Fblank range on a doorstep in Talbot
OL,12,FGreen on 9 March 2025 and died shortly
OL,13,Fafterwards.
OL,15,FA jury at Cardiff Crown Court returned
OL,16,Fa verdict that Joshua Gordon, Jordan
OL,17,FMills Smith, Melissa Quailey Dashper
OL,18,Fand Kristina Ginova were all found
OL,19,Fguilty of murder for the roles they
OL,20,Fplayed in Ms Penney's death. One, Tony
OL,21,FPorter, was found not guilty of murder.
